<plot>Henry, the caretaker of a small housing complex, becomes distraught when he hears sounds of domestic abuse coming from the apartment of a young couple. Choosing at first to ignore the sounds, Henry's apathy becomes intolerable when he develops a brief but meaningful connection with the young woman. Bearing his own emotional scars from a horrific childhood at the hands of an abusive father, Henry enlists the help of a friend and decides to intervene.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?009967</url></doc>
